This paper deals with algorithms for computing geometric properties of polygonal domains, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The algorithms presented in the paper involve data structures and graph algorithms, which are also relevant to the sub-categories of cs.DS and cs.GT. The paper also involves some combinatorial analysis, which is relevant to the sub-category of cs.DM. Finally, the paper involves numerical optimization, which is relevant to the sub-category of cs.NA.
